message.body: AHHHHH! Got such weird drunk texts from ex David last night! Oh no!
What kind of weird??? Like sexy weird???!!!
He was saying stuff like he loved me! In Spanish.
And that I was beautiful. And something about living in the sea that didn't make sense.
What a trouble maker.
I think I only got part of your text...can you resend?? I don't wanna miss a thing!
He was saying stuff like he loved me! In Spanish.
He was saying stuff like he loved me! In Spanish.
And that I was beautiful. And something about living in the sea that didn't make sense.
What????!!! That's wild!
What is he up to???!
He's being a little trouble maker.
Has he expressed these kinds of feelings before? How does it make you feel?
No! He's just being weepy. What a turd. I told him eh better check himself before he wrecks himself!
He probably asked someone out and got rejected.
Oh man...that's ridiculous!
Are you gonna hang with Lo this weekend?
Hot yoga
Hahaha hell no I'm not doing hot yoga! :) I told her I could hang Friday and get some food and drink. You gonna hang?
If you are, please say Friday...
Yeah I'll do Friday after work. Text me when you guys go. I want to take it easy Saturday.
It's my first Saturday off in a long time
Cool! Yeah, I can't hang Saturday and gotta work most of the day Sunday. Lo said she's getting in around 8:30 in Friday so I'm gonna meet up with her then!
Sounds good!
I love you so much and you are so handsome and wonderful! :)
Omg. Stop.
Hahaha oh shit...I meant to send that to julian! Woopsies.
Hahaha
I wasn't trying to pull a david...did you tell hunter about that??
Noway! Never gonna.
That's probably a good idea!
I'm drunk on wine!
Oh man I wish I was drunk on wine!
You could be! I'm alone at home...no problem!
Where's Julian at class??
Yeah! He got home at like 9:45! Drunk mama night!
